lative; line-height: 34px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 24px; color: white;&quot;&gt;The FY WG is a miniaturized version of our best-selling gimbal, offering exceptional stabilization technology in a wearable form factor for action cameras. It is lightweight, yet feature-rich, and capable of capturing immersive and fully stabilized footages.&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 1920px; height:637px; background: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/WG_03.jpg) no-repeat&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot;width: 870px; height:557px; margin: 40px 525px;&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;embed src=&quot;http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMTI3ODI2OTAxNg==/v.swf&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; quality=&quot;high&quot; width=&quot;870&quot; height=&quot;557&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot; allowscriptaccess=&quot;always&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot;&gt; \n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 700px; height: 600px; background: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/WG_04.jpg); padding: 13px 610px 150px;&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div id=&quot;my3DPics&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; height: 600px; width: 700px; background-image: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/images/1.png);&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div id=&quot;my3DPics-loading&quot; style=&quot;position:absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; bottom: 0;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;img src=&quot;/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/images/1.png&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; width: 1920px; height: 569px; background: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/WG_05.jpg) no-repeat; &quot;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; width: 515px; height: 656px; background: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/WG/WG_06.jpg) no-repeat; padding: 40px 400px 0px 1005px; &quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-align: ce