(18, 3, 'DOS 惯性姿态平衡仪', 'DoS是主要针对航模初学着和提高飞行技巧，飞行安全性，帮助飞行操作而设计的一款可以适应多种平台的自动驾驶仪。 DoS包括10自由度的传感器，三轴数字加速度计、三轴数字陀螺仪、三轴数字磁场计和高精度气压计，体积更小巧，稳定性更高。\n  \n  \n  \n', 'DOS惯性姿态平衡仪', '2015-07-23 14:37:44', 0, 1, 4, 0, 24, 10, '', '2016-01-23 00:00:00', NULL, 1, 0, 0, 127, '', 0, '/TAMCDN/pic/512ae56afa7dd693306.jpg_240x240.jpg', '[/TAMCDN/pic/d35aba0d07b227f0183.jpg];\n[/TAMCDN/pic/18f04cf02ee6f65b137.jpg];\n[/TAMCDN/pic/e42014bec16d5a52205.jpg];\n[/TAMCDN/pic/93a65e60c43263f5129.jpg];\n[/TAMCDN/pic/4274465e49bbc05d122.jpg];\n[/TAMCDN/pic/395fcdbbe6e2d711132.jpg];', '', '{【说明书】 FY-DOS固定翼安装使用说明, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/6184cc8e0e130b5a320.pdf, 说明书下载};\n{【固件升级软件】 FY飞控&amp;平衡仪固件升级软件 V2.04及使用说明, 2015-07-24, /TAMCDN/doc/a0454535e324b49f172.rar, 固件升级软件};\n{【固件】 FY-DOS固定翼固件V1.25, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/cf1a569222cb526f338.rar, 固件下载};\n{【设置软件】 FY-DOS 设置软件 V1.1, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/01754984d01fc2d6192.rar, 设置软件};\n{【GCS】 GCS 5.11 For DOS 地面站软件, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/1df31a315fb2c7d448.rar};\n{【GCS】 2D版地面站软件 FY GCS 4.12, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/e0017b6ae10827ad388.rar};\n{【GCS】 地图制作软件 FYGscreen (Map Maker)【使用2D地图时使用】, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/012596c0a4b22991308.rar};\n{【GCS】 Google Earth 4.3, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/eaa09bd13bf7dee9258.rar};\n{【GCS】 GoogleEarth plugin (Google Earth插件), 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/01154afd6f14bc0f33.rar};\n{【OSD】 OSD相关下载, 2015-07-25, /TAMCDN/doc/9f29bc898dfddcd5210.rar};\n{【USB线驱动】 飞宇新版USB线驱动下载, 2015-07-16, /TAMCDN/doc/4d014439915571fb8.rar, USB驱动下载};\n', '', '&lt;script&gt;\n$(document).ready(function(){\n	$(&quot;#my3DPics&quot;).vc3dEye({\n		imagePath:&quot;/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/Dos/images/&quot;,\n		totalImages:40,\n		imageExtension:&quot;png&quot;\n	});\n});\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; width: 1200px; height: 230px; padding: 40px 360px 0px&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;DOS Module&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; position: relative; line-height: 27px; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;DOS Module is designed for beginners who seek to improve their flying experiences. &lt;br&gt;\n    The module improves flight stability and provides adaptive assistance for new pilots.&lt;br&gt;\n    DOS integrates a three-axis accelerometer, a three-axis gyroscope, &lt;br&gt;\n    a three-axis magnetometer and a highly accurate barometer into a compact module.&lt;br&gt;\n    The small physical dimension reduces weight impact on aircraft’s stability.&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;position: relative; width: 600px; height: 500px; background: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/DOS/DOS_03.png) bottom; padding: 0 620px 20px 700px;&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div id=&quot;my3DPics&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; top: -30px; height: 500px; width: 600px; background-image: url(/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/DOS/images/1.png);&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div id=&quot;my3DPics-loading&quot; style=&quot;position:absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; bottom: 0;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;img src=&quot;/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/DOS/images/1.png&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 1200px; height: auto; padding: 0px 360px 0px;&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Manual Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;DOS will not assist in any aircraft operation. All control and maneuver will be perform manually by the user&lt;br&gt;\n    (similar to a regular RC scheme).&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Auto Stabilization Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;DOS will ensure the aircraft maintains its horizontal level under any weather condition. This mode will &lt;br&gt;\n    deliver a significantly better experience to new pilots by reducing manual user interventions. If at any &lt;br&gt;\n    point the user feels that he/she is losing control, pressing the throttle steadily and releasing the &lt;br&gt;\n    directional sticks will automatically correct the aircraft’s flight level.&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;3D Flight Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;Stabilized assisted flight. Releasing the directional control will lock the current flight stance. Smooth &lt;br&gt;\n    flight path and maneuvers can be easily achieved.&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Fixed Path (Altitude/Direction) Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;In this mode, aircraft’s altitude and direction will be locked and sustained. As the user releases the &lt;br&gt;\n    directional stick, the aircraft will maintain the flight’s direction and altitude by autocorrecting any &lt;br&gt;\n    external influences. &lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Auto Circling Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;DOS maintains the current altitude, while performing a counter clockwise circling flight path. However this is &lt;br&gt;\n    not a fixed location circling mechanism (as wind can cause the aircraft to deviate from its original path).&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Auto Return to Home (RTH) Mode&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;When this mode is activated, the aircraft will maintain its current attitude and follow its path to return to &lt;br&gt;\n    its initial starting point. Once it reaches the starting point, the aircraft will maintain a circling flight path &lt;br&gt;\n    around the location.&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Ground Control Software&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;Flight statistics, flight path and other settings can be configured by using the ground control software&lt;br&gt;\n    (Must connected to Data Radio to apply settings)&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 1200px; height: auto; padding: 0px 360px 0px;&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot;padding: 50px 0px 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/DOS/DOS_05.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; height=&quot;260&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 40px;&quot;&gt;Compatible with Hornet FY-OSD Module and Data Radio&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div style=&quot; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0px 100px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px;&quot;&gt;DOS provides an interface for connecting the FY Data Radio and OSD Module. By connecting both devices, the &lt;br&gt;\n    following functionalities are supported:&lt;br&gt;\n    ● First Person View (FPV) —— Can be connected to Hornet OSD to relay video signal transmitted back from the &lt;br&gt;\n    aircraft and to provide a first person perspective view. Fixed Path Mode and Auto Return to Home Mode assist in &lt;br&gt;\n    providing a smoother FPV experience.&lt;br&gt;\n    &lt;br&gt;\n    ● Real-time Monitoring —— Real-time monitor on flying statistics. Data Radio can further extends the remote &lt;br&gt;\n    control range. Ground Control Software can adjust different settings on the fly.&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;', '/Tangram/Theme/Feiyu/images/DOS/FY-DOS.pdf', '&lt;table width=&quot;1200&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;尺寸重量&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;47mm x 30mm x 11mm（不包括电线）：25g&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;适用机型&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;目前可用于固定翼飞机戒者升级固件后用于其它飞行器和设备的控制\n标准版 DoS 适用以下机型：&lt;br&gt; \n1.  正常布局固定翼飞机；&lt;br&gt; \n2.  飞翼布局带方向舵的飞机；&lt;br&gt; \n3.  飞翼布局无方向舵飞机； &lt;br&gt;\n4.  无副翼飞机；&lt;br&gt;\n5.  带副翼 V 尾飞机；&lt;br&gt; \n6.  无副翼 V 尾飞机； &lt;br&gt;\n7.  其他机型是否适用请収邮件到此邮箱迕行咨询: service@feiyu-tech.com。&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;调参软件安装要求&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;Windows XP SP3；Windows 7；Windows8&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;设备功能&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;1、DoS平衡仪单独工作时具备的功能：手动模式、自动平衡、3D飞行、定高定向、自动盘旋&lt;br&gt;\n2、DoS平衡仪连接 GPS模块后具备的功能：定高定向、自动返航、自动盘旋、GCS软件&lt;br&gt;\n3、可连接Hornet-OSD 和数传电台：First Person View (FPV)、实时监测&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;工作电压&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;4.0V~6.0V&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;电流&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;50mA（5V）&lt;/td&gt;\n          &lt;/tr&gt;\n          &lt;tr&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;控制频率&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n            &lt;td&gt;400Hz&lt;/td&g